Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the deployment process for the mytaxi_AndroidCI system:

```plantuml
@startuml freenowtech_AndroidCI

actor Developer
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "Jenkins Master" as Jenkins
participant "Docker Host" as DockerHost
participant "Android SDK Container" as AndroidContainer
participant "Artifact Repository" as ArtifactRepo

Developer -> Git : Push code changes
Git -> Jenkins : Trigger build
Jenkins -> DockerHost : Request container
DockerHost -> AndroidContainer : Create container
Jenkins -> AndroidContainer : Execute build job
AndroidContainer -> AndroidContainer : Compile code
AndroidContainer -> AndroidContainer : Run tests
AndroidContainer -> AndroidContainer : Generate APK
AndroidContainer -> Jenkins : Return build results
Jenkins -> ArtifactRepo : Store APK
Jenkins -> Developer : Notify build status

@enduml
```